      <ul>
        <li><strong>Data collection</strong> — We collect only the information you voluntarily provide (e.g., email for newsletter subscription). We do not sell or share personal data with third parties.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies</strong> — We use essential cookies for site functionality and analytics cookies to understand readership patterns. No tracking cookies from third-party advertisers are used.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — We use privacy-respecting analytics to understand which content serves our readers best. No personally identifiable information is collected through analytics.</li>
        <li><strong>Newsletter</strong> — Newsletter subscribers may unsubscribe at any time. Email addresses are not shared with any third party.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="terms">
